## Animation Config

All 4 layers animate independently using `TimelineView(.animation)`:

| Layer | Animation | Config |
|-------|-----------|--------|
| **Background** | Slow breathing scale | ±0.4% @ 0.25Hz |
| **Accent** | Opacity + scale pulse | 75-100% opacity, ±0.65% scale @ 0.4Hz |
| **Figure** | Breathing + float | ±0.8% scale, ±3px y-offset |
| **Foreground** | Opacity shimmer | 88-100% @ 0.55Hz |
| **Ambient Glow** | Radial gradient pulse | 12-28% opacity @ 0.35Hz |

